description: This skill allows you to interact with your WigWag system with Alexa using voice commands. Turn your lights on or off, trigger moods, set up rules and more. You must have a WigWag account and WigWag relay before you can connect it to an Amazon Echo.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask wigwag to turn everything on
Alexa, ask wigwag to list the moods
Alexa, ask wigwag to set brightness to 50 percent
name: WigWag Skill
shortDescription: Use Alexa to control your WigWag system
